==Chinese==
===[[Mandarin]]===
[[Pinyin]]: liú dé qīngshān zài, bùpà méi chái shāo

===Etymology===
Literally: As long as the green mountains are there, one need not worry about firewood.

===Proverb===
'''[[留]][[得]][[青山]][[在]]，[[不怕]][[沒]][[柴]][[燒]]'''

# While there's life, there's hope.

===Alternate forms===
[[留得青山在，不怕没柴烧]] ([[Simplified Chinese]])

===Related terms===
*[[不到黃河心不死]]
*[[不見棺材不掉淚]]

